{"snp5.6:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.6 ","snp5.6:0.2":"Dhotakamanavapuccha ","snp5.6:1.1":"“Pucchami tam bhagava bruhi metam, ","snp5.6:1.2":"(iccayasma dhotako) ","snp5.6:1.3":"Vacabhikankhami mahesi tuyham; ","snp5.6:1.4":"Tava sutvana nigghosam, ","snp5.6:1.5":"Sikkhe nibbanamattano”. ","snp5.6:2.1":"“Tenahatappam karohi, ","snp5.6:2.2":"(dhotakati bhagava) ","snp5.6:2.3":"Idheva nipako sato; ","snp5.6:2.4":"Ito sutvana nigghosam, ","snp5.6:2.5":"Sikkhe nibbanamattano”. ","snp5.6:3.1":"“Passamaham devamanussaloke, ","snp5.6:3.2":"Akincanam brahmanamiriyamanam; ","snp5.6:3.3":"Tam tam namassami samantacakkhu, ","snp5.6:3.4":"Pamunca mam sakka kathankathahi”. ","snp5.6:4.1":"“Naham sahissami pamocanaya, ","snp5.6:4.2":"Kathankathim dhotaka kanci loke; ","snp5.6:4.3":"Dhammanca settham abhijanamano, ","snp5.6:4.4":"Evam tuvam oghamimam taresi”. ","snp5.6:5.1":"“Anusasa brahme karunayamano, ","snp5.6:5.2":"Vivekadhammam yamaham vijannam; ","snp5.6:5.3":"Yathaham akasova abyapajjamano, ","snp5.6:5.4":"Idheva santo asito careyyam”. ","snp5.6:6.1":"“Kittayissami te santim, ","snp5.6:6.2":"(dhotakati bhagava) ","snp5.6:6.3":"Ditthe dhamme anitiham; ","snp5.6:6.4":"Yam viditva sato caram, ","snp5.6:6.5":"Tare loke visattikam”. ","snp5.6:7.1":"“Tancaham abhinandami, ","snp5.6:7.2":"mahesi santimuttamam; ","snp5.6:7.3":"Yam viditva sato caram, ","snp5.6:7.4":"tare loke visattikam”. ","snp5.6:8.1":"“Yam kinci sampajanasi, ","snp5.6:8.2":"(dhotakati bhagava) ","snp5.6:8.3":"Uddham adho tiriyancapi majjhe; ","snp5.6:8.4":"Etam viditva sangoti loke, ","snp5.6:8.5":"Bhavabhavaya makasi tanhan”ti. ","snp5.6:8.6":"Dhotakamanavapuccha pancami. "}